protothickbox.js

Original : ThickBox 3.1 (http://jquery.com/demo/thickbox/)
License  : MIT-style license.

Modified by : Spookies Labs (http://labs.spookies.jp)
Depends on : prototype.js 1.6 or later + effects.js


*how to use

<link href="/stylesheets/thickbox.css" media="screen" rel="Stylesheet" type="text/css" />
<script src="/javascripts/prototype.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
<script src="/javascripts/effects.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
<script src="/javascripts/protothickbox.js" type="text/javascript"></script>

It is the same as the original.



